== Inventory

Inventory system for tracking computer systems.


== Requirements

1. mongodb - http://www.mongodb.org/

2. Rails 3 - http://rubyonrails.org/


== Getting Started

1. /path-to-mongodb/bin/mongod # start mongodb 

2. git clone git://github.com/Druwerd/inventory.git # checkout source code

3. cd inventory && bundle install # install gem dependencies

4. rails s # start the web server
